item.title: 300. Happy 300th Episode To Us! Hearing Your Messages Beans
item.description:
It's been 300 WHOLE episodes of DYFM so my producer Elise put together some voice memos from you my beautiful beans!

Plus I go through my favourite episodes of the pod (so far duh), where a new bean should start if you’re recommending the show to a friend, and what I'm manifesting for the next 300 episodes!
